description:
Dr. Barry Harris jazz workshop (January 2020) with Cecile Mclorin-Salvant (vocal) & Sullivan Fortner (piano) 
There were so many musicians learning beautiful jazz music, and we had great time with such super famous musicians like them, too... :) 

巨匠バリーハリス氏のもとに、グラミー受賞でとっても売れっ子のヴォーカリスト セシルさんと、ピアニストのサリバンさんも訪れ、お二人の共演で「Body & Soul」の演奏が聴けた素敵な日でした！（2020年1月21日撮影＠ニューヨーク市内のスタジオにて）
title: Dr. Barry Harris jazz workshop (January 2020) with Cecile Mclorin-Salvant & Sullivan Fortner
fulltitle: Dr. Barry Harris jazz workshop (January 2020) with Cecile Mclorin-Salvant & Sullivan Fortner
